props.title: Total used file descriptors
props.query: SELECT average(`rabbitmq.node.fileDescriptorsTotalUsed`) FROM Metric WHERE `entityGuid` = '{{entity.id}}' TIMESERIES auto

props.title: File descriptors used sockets
props.query: SELECT average(`rabbitmq.node.fileDescriptorsUsedSockets`) FROM Metric WHERE `entityGuid` = '{{entity.id}}' TIMESERIES auto

props.title: Total memory usage
props.query: SELECT average(`rabbitmq.node.totalMemoryUsedInBytes`) FROM Metric WHERE `entityGuid` = '{{entity.id}}' TIMESERIES auto
